  --- Negative secure-renegotiation reachability checks.
  --- Scenarios 44 and 45 intentionally produce nil.  They remove the
  --- renegotiation-info extension from the ServerHello/ClientHello path and
  --- require progress to processServerHelloV2; the RFC checks should reject
  --- the malformed renegotiation state before that process step is reachable.

  op behaviorDeviationSpecification44 : -> Set{BehaviorDVSpec} .
  eq behaviorDeviationSpecification44 =
     {'scen44, ruleLabel('buildServerHelloV2), remove(#renegotiation-info)} .

